{"tid":1266661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抱抱傳播愛的行動 正式啟動#like#","createTime":"2019-06-29T15:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T15:11:49.000Z","uid":167355,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f43843548b82d2474103d56615ed102992db7770","tid":1266661,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:07:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">無論有幾多白色恐怖，無論有幾多無力感</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋都係手足</span></span> <br />\n我地唔可以放棄身邊任何一個！ 如果你相信我，你可唔可以幫我做一樣野？<br />\n無論幾時，係邊度，見到香港人<br />\n講句<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「加油」附加一個抱抱</span></span></strong> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為如果你抱嘅個個人，有想死既念頭，有灰心既念頭，我希望呢個行動可以喚醒佢</span>，等佢知道每一個香港人都好需要佢！<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我愛你地啊香港人</span>！</span><br />\n<br />\n我第一次出po，我同樣覺得好無力，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係，我地一個地不能少！</span> ，請尊重任何一個人！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2019年6月29 抱抱傳播愛的行動 正式啟動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"60680e33d0248a8408f5f1e1ccbec5c63a1c7c77","tid":1266661,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:07:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fdfa5b035a28ae2e01a4ebcd4233497f534c2a7","tid":1266661,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:07:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d090dc1fb32f4d59cef25b97db70b9e3dcd9a49","tid":1266661,"uid":230039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:10:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3185bb4a938ed8af37c293ad7766c047aa83f0f2","tid":1266661,"uid":69177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:11:49.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal